Lets see what I can get from memory
2 bracers of loyalty to vox
executioners hood
Lizzie tribal mask
azure sleeves
drakescale legs
wolf fur slippers
Flowing black silk sash
black pearl choker
cured silk mantle
cured silk gloves
white wolf hide cloak
2 Obsidian bead hoops
1 jagged band
1 fire emerald ring

I also keep a crown of the froglock kings and another jagged band on me for
when I am tanking or pulling for the higher AC. I thinks thats all did I
miss any slots?

Kizmet Bayashi
39th level monk
Da`Kor
E-Marr
